  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🤩 In Popmoji you combine two of the same emojis to create bigger emojis until the cycle is finished. But the bigger they get...the less space you'll have to place them!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >😲 Strategically drop emojis in the box to match and create bigger ones!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🥶 Use abilities to create crazier scenarios, and increase your chances of survival!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏆 Fight for the best spot on the leaderboard!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎮 12 different game modes </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Includes 11 different emojis in the cycle and 27 different abilities!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by the viral Suika Game; now with a new coat of paint and abilities to make it feel like the next weird mixed-genre Vampire Survivors!</p>",
